				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">A reminder, what occurs on the Test Server is not a guarantee that it will be put into production, BUT THEN AGAIN it is not a guarantee that it WONT BE put into production.
<br />

<br />
I was in OOT getting my Mage Character some experience, some pp's and some toes for other mages seeking to get their focus items.
<br />

<br />
Now Gornit is a 6 minute spawn, has been for as long as I can remember.
<br />

<br />
Sometime recently, Gornit has been put on a RANDOM spawn timer.  So far I think the time can be between 6 minutes and 12 minutes.
<br />

<br />
How would it strike you all, if MoB's were placed on a random spawn timer, rather than a fixed spawn timer.
<br />

<br />
PS:
<br />

<br />
This could be an attempt to stop players from farming both the Sea Furies and Gornit, allowing the peer level players to have access to Gornit.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
